title: Nothing Substantial - Insubordinate
description:
CD release  with Matt Fassler / Ryan Fassler / Zac Hunter/ Ryan Wasterlain

4 piece skaterock band from Los Gatos, CA.

Active from 1996 - 1999

Members went on to other bands such as: Agression (nardcore), Riff-Raff, Fury 66, Trapt, No Common Sense, Buried at Birth, Permanent Black, Summer of Glaciers, Nerve Agents, Jim Jones Brigade, Manson Family Feud, At Risk, Save Yourself, Dead Set.

For fans of the early Epi-Fat sound. 

.m4a format
